{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844328818,"sessionID":"ses_2876e587fffeh7wQuwhTosOkay","part":{"id":"prt_d7891fec2001TFGOy4qXDzdJwX","messageID":"msg_d7891eee6001SdwZriZshRmj26","sessionID":"ses_2876e587fffeh7wQuwhTosOkay","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_a0f0d18f8eb042ebb5196c7d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"AR-006|lifecycle|garbage.*collect|idle|expire","path":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration"},"output":"Found 56 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-006-sandbox-deletion-lifecycle/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Design\n  Line 7: | AR | AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 |\n  Line 33:     → 1. ListInactiveSandboxes(idleTimeout=15m)\n  Line 34:     → 2. ListExpiredSandboxes(expiresAt=now)\n  Line 123:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n  Line 134: // pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go\n  Line 152:     CleanupReasonIdleTimeout SandboxCleanupReason = \"idle_timeout\"\n  Line 155:     CleanupReasonExpired SandboxCleanupReason = \"expired\"\n  Line 323: // pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go\n  Line 374:     idleThreshold := now.Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout)\n  Line 375:     expiredThreshold := now\n  Line 377:     // 1. Cleanup idle sandboxes\n  Line 378:     idleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n  Line 382:         for _, sandbox := range idleSandboxes {\n  Line 387:     // 2. Cleanup expired sandboxes\n  Line 388:     expiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n  Line 390:         log.Errorf(\"Failed to list expired sandboxes: %v\", err)\n  Line 392:         for _, sandbox := range expiredSandboxes {\n  Line 471:     // Initialize garbage collector\n  Line 486:     // Start garbage collector\n  Line 493:     // Stop garbage collector\n  Line 672: // pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go\n  Line 677:     idleSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n  Line 679:             SessionID:    \"idle-session-1\",\n  Line 680:             SandboxID:    \"idle-sandbox-1\",\n  Line 685:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, int64(16)).Return(idleSandboxes, nil)\n  Line 686:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\").Return(nil)\n  Line 689:     sandboxObj := buildUnstructuredSandbox(\"idle-sandbox-1\", \"default\")\n  Line 700:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\")\n  Line 706:     expiredSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n  Line 708:             SessionID:    \"expired-session-1\",\n  Line 709:             SandboxID:    \"expired-sandbox-1\",\n  Line 714:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, int64(16)).Return(expiredSandboxes, nil)\n  Line 715:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\").Return(nil)\n  Line 718:     sandboxObj := buildUnstructuredSandbox(\"expired-sandbox-1\", \"default\")\n  Line 759: // pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go\n  Line 846: - GarbageCollector：idle 清理、expired 清理、K8s NotFound 处理\n  Line 856:   garbage_collector.go       — garbageCollector struct, gcLoop, tick, deleteSandbox\n  Line 857:   garbage_collector_test.go  — GC unit tests\n  Line 890: - 清理原因（manual/idle_timeout/expired）\n  Line 935:     // ListInactiveSandboxes lists sandboxes idle longer than threshold.\n  Line 938:     // ListExpiredSandboxes lists sandboxes past their expiresAt.\n  Line 1018: | 功能 | AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器) | AR-006 (Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理) |\n  Line 1030: AR-005 负责 sandbox 的创建和初始化，AR-006 负责 sandbox 的删除和全生命周期管理。\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/tasks.md:\n  Line 58:   - Set annotations: idle-timeout\n  Line 60:   - Set replicas=1, lifecycle.shutdownTime=now+MaxSessionDuration\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md:\n  Line 223:   - `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout`: SessionTimeout 字符串（默认 \"15m\"）\n  Line 227:   - `lifecycle.shutdownTime`: `now + MaxSessionDuration`（默认 8h）\n  Line 576:   garbage_collector.go   — garbageCollector, gcLoop\n  Line 586:   garbage_collector_test.go\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md:\n  Line 222:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n  Line 329:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey  = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n  Line 465: - AgentRuntime: sandbox name `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`, UUID session ID, ports from `spec.Ports`, TTL/idle from `MaxSessionDuration` / `SessionTimeout` when non-nil.\n  Line 467: - `buildSandboxObject`: APIVersion `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind `Sandbox`, labels include `managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`, annotation `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey` = idle duration string, lifecycle `ShutdownTime` = now+TTL, `Replicas: ptr.To[int32](1)`.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md:\n  Line 4: Orchestrate agent sandboxes via Kubernetes CRDs (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter), a Gin HTTP API (workload manager), session persistence, garbage collection, and optional service-account authentication.\n  Line 155: The system SHALL run a background goroutine tick every 15 seconds; each tick SHALL use a context timeout of 2 minutes; SHALL query inactive sessions with cutoff `now - 15m` and batch limit 16; SHALL query expired sessions with `before = now` and batch limit 16; SHALL merge lists and delete each unique workload then remove store entry by session ID.","metadata":{"matches":56,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-006|lifecycle|garbage.*collect|idle|expire","time":{"start":1775844328809,"end":1775844328817}}}}
